  "text": "Since cellular water content reflects the efficiency of ATP-dependent active transport [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , we assessed the effects of LPD on placental water content. Reduced oncotic pressure resulting from protein deficiency might also be associated with excess fluid.",
